                </div><br /><br />    
                <p>Life can be stressful, and what better way to relax than with a great massage? Or, if you want to remove the signs of stress and have a vibrant look all year round, a facial can help you achieve a healthy-looking complexion.</p>
                <p>Both of these services and more are available at Blue Fountain Day Spa in Green Brook, which opened in October of 2016. The manager, Lin Shen, is very knowledgeable about the body and believes that massages and facials not only help you feel and look better, but can also improve your overall well-being. She owned a spa in China for 15 years, and Chinese medicine is the foundation of what she practices. When she started working in spas in the United States 4 &frac12; years ago, she brought these skills with her. Lin has been with Blue Fountain Day Spa since the day it opened, and she trains all the staff to ensure that they are following the practices she believes work the best. </p>
